Note: ============================================================================
Note: RFC 4231 Test Case 6: long-key (131 bytes of 0xaa), short message
Note: Exercises the key-longer-than-block-size hash-down code path.
Note: Expected HMAC-SHA256 (correct vector per Python hashlib + OpenSSL):
Note:   60e43159 1ee0b67f 0d8a26aa cbf5b77f
Note:   8e0bc621 3728c514 0546040f 0ee37f54
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "test_hmac_sha256_rfc4231_case6_longkey" that takes results as Integer returns Integer:
    T.begin_suite(results, "hmac_sha256 RFC 4231 case 6 long key")

