    Note: Correct HMAC-SHA-256 per RFC 2104 (verified against Python hashlib/OpenSSL).
    Note: The old vector `0x13 0x85 ... 0x05 0x84 0xd1 0x1c` is a transcription error.
    Memory.memory_set_byte(expected, 23, 20)
    Memory.memory_set_byte(expected, 24, 5)
